---
import Prose from "@components/Prose.astro";
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  pageTitle="Now | Hyun Don Moon"
  pageDescription="What I'm up to right now"
>
  <Prose>
    <h1>Now</h1>

    <p>
      This page is inspired by Derek Sivers' <a
        href="https://nownownow.com/about"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">/now pages</a
      > movement. It's a simple concept: a page that tells you what someone is focused
      on at this point in their life.
    </p>

    <section>
      <h3>December, 2025</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Reading</strong>: After finishing Robin Hobb's <em>Assassin's Quest</em>, I've started her next series, the <em>Liveship Traders Trilogy</em>.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Learning</strong>: I'm studying Elm and Python to explore functional programming and delve deeper into AI concepts.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Gaming</strong>: I'm thoroughly enjoying playing <em>The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild</em> before heading to bed each night.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Travel & Hobbies</strong>: I'm planning a family trip to Sapporo next month and bought a used Sony RX100 M3 camera to capture our time there.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Projects</strong>: I've started experimenting with Obsidian as a tool to help organize my thoughts and notes.
          </p>
        </li>
         <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Other</strong>: I'm currently recovering from having three wisdom teeth removed.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top:2em; font-size:0.9em; color: #666;">
        This page was updated automatically using n8n & Google Gemini.
      </p>
    </section>
  </Prose>
</BaseLayout>